CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.byquarter22021
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'BYQUARTER/',
	DATA_SOURCE = [raysynapsemgdvnetdlacctfs_raysynapsemgdvnetdlacct_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseDelimitedTextFormat]
	)
AS
SELECT
    [YEAR], [QUARTER], [ACTIVE], [CEASED]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://raysynapsemgdvnetdlacct.dfs.core.windows.net/raysynapsemgdvnetdlacctfs/DCC/CannabisAccountSitesByQuarter.csv',
        FORMAT = 'CSV',
        PARSER_VERSION = '2.0',
        HEADER_ROW = TRUE
    ) AS [result]
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.byquarter
GO
